text: José Oyarzabal (born 13 February 1970) is a French international rower. He won a silver medal in eights at the 1988 World Junior Rowing Championships, a silver medal in coxless fours at the 1990 World Rowing Championships, a silver medal in eights at the 1990 World Rowing Championships, and a bronze medal in coxless fours at the 1992 World Rowing Championships. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:French male rowers Category:World Rowing Championships medalists for France
